{"tid":1767823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有線：消息指行政長官林鄭月娥本月中將向中共領導人述職","createTime":"2019-12-03T14:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T03:46:20.000Z","uid":212626,"like":58,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"13a7c1329731a10054fc49c731b3186a7b7fbc61","tid":1767823,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】消息指行政長官林鄭月娥本月中將向中央領導人述職。<br />\n<br />\n消息指按初步計劃，林鄭月娥本月16日將向領導人述職，按往年慣例，林鄭月娥在北京會分別獲國務院總理李克強及國家主席習近平親自接見<br />\n。林鄭月娥會呈交述職報告，預料她會匯報近日區議會選舉結果及止暴制亂的進展。<br />\n<br />\n香港自六月以來的社會動盪至今仍未平息，習近平十一月初在上海接見了林鄭月娥，指中央對她高度信任，並充分肯定她和團隊的工作。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/12438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F12438&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=3c5d2f03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F12438&h=1298bbcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/12438</a>"},{"pid":"4f748e91a3477a3d76ec289368695dc723cc058e","tid":1767823,"uid":79117,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"有咩可以報告，一鑊粥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14c406c075c3152e1a45c33f0ea01e1d9729eae","tid":1767823,"uid":146285,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"咁就要係14,15號個weekend賀下佢"},{"pid":"00aca6b67d65911ca71f57c4042889fdec1eed0a","tid":1767823,"uid":78039,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"叫傻強去就得啦"},{"pid":"eeddf82145fffb2797b61c137434b9f131f570fc","tid":1767823,"uid":272292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f58ce50165eb15a9704773ad9eb38c80bfb60800","tid":1767823,"uid":162008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:04:05.000